### Gaps Summary

Two issues block full goal achievement:

**Gap 1 — Netlify not deployed (blocker for success criterion 4):**
The Plan 03 SUMMARY explicitly records Task 2 as a human-action checkpoint awaiting user action. The GitHub remote (`https://github.com/brenmac23/uplift-compare.git`) has the latest commits (c97d6b1 is HEAD on origin/master), the build is verified green (282KB bundle, no errors), and netlify.toml is correctly configured. The only missing step is the human-initiated Netlify connection and deploy. This is the only fully automated verifiable blocker.

**Gap 2 — "Titanfall Legacy" franchise name (warning for success criterion 1):**
49 of 50 project names are original genre-evocative titles. Seed-049 is named "Titanfall Legacy" — Titanfall is an active EA/Respawn Entertainment registered trademark for a video-game franchise. The PROJ-01 requirement and Phase 2 plan explicitly forbid real franchise names. This is a straightforward rename. The automated distribution tests do not check for franchise name collisions, so this passed all tests.

Both gaps are addressable: Gap 1 requires human action; Gap 2 requires a one-line rename in `src/data/seedProjects.ts` (line 2330).

